name: Zainab
greetingText: Happy Birthday to a special person who is bringing so much joy to my heart. I am thankful for every moment we spend together, and I wish our happiness never ends
wishText: I hope your Birthday will always be as beautiful and full of love as you are. You deserve only the best, and I will always wish that for you Happy Birthday In Arrears Zainab Bahmore Adukemi! ;)
